<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Lakshay Chawla | Blog</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="rough/styles.css">
</head>

<body>
    <div class="HEADER">
        <div class="SIGNATUREHEAD" id="LOGO">
            <a href="#"><img src="rough/mySign.png" alt="My Name Logo" srcset=""></a>
        </div>

        <div class="NAVBAR">

            <ul class="LINKLIST" id="LINKLIST">
                <a href="/">
                    <li class="LINK" id="HOMELINK">HOME</li>
                </a>
                <a href="/about">
                    <li class="LINK" id="ABTLINK">ABOUT</li>
                </a>
                <a href="/contact">
                    <li class="LINK" id="CONTACTLINK">CONTACT ME</li>
                </a>
                <a href="/newsletter">
                    <li class="LINK" id="NLETTER">NEWSLETTER</li>
                </a>

            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="PGHEAD">
        <h1><a href="/">BLOG</a></h1>
        <p id="NEWBLOGLINK"><a href="/articles/new">Write a new blog</a></p>

    </div>


    <div class="BLOGPOST">
        <h2>Title</h2>
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" fill="currentColor" class="OPTIONSMENU bi bi-three-dots-vertical" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
            <path d="M9.5 13a1.5 1.5 0 1 1-3 0 1.5 1.5 0 0 1 3 0zm0-5a1.5 1.5 0 1 1-3 0 1.5 1.5 0 0 1 3 0zm0-5a1.5 1.5 0 1 1-3 0 1.5 1.5 0 0 1 3 0z"/>
        </svg>
        <p class="POSTDATE">Aug 12, 2021</p>
        <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Molestiae minima earum libero magnam aliquid vitae non similique temporibus optio animi consequatur, quaerat, enim, amet expedita. Eveniet aliquam voluptate recusandae repellendus ut, ducimus
            rerum quibusdam accusamus nostrum ad, porro optio amet. Facilis numquam alias fugiat nesciunt unde? <a href="#">Read more...</a></p>

    </div>

    <% articles.forEach(article => { %>
        <div class="BLOGPOST">
            <h2>
                <%= article.title %>
            </h2>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" fill="currentColor" class="OPTIONSMENU bi bi-three-dots-vertical" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                <path d="M9.5 13a1.5 1.5 0 1 1-3 0 1.5 1.5 0 0 1 3 0zm0-5a1.5 1.5 0 1 1-3 0 1.5 1.5 0 0 1 3 0zm0-5a1.5 1.5 0 1 1-3 0 1.5 1.5 0 0 1 3 0z"/>
            </svg>
            <p class="POSTDATE">
                <%= article.builtOn.toLocaleDateString() %>
            </p>
            <p>
                <%= article.blogPost %> <a href="#">Read more...</a></p>
            <p class="POSTDATE">
                <%= article.authorName %>
            </p>

        </div>
        <% }) %>
</body>

</html>